name: 60 Second Santa
description:
60 Second Santa! Quickly! There is no time to waste! Santa has presents that need delivering and time is almost out!!!

Use the arrow key's to move and the space-bar to yeet a present!
Quickly make it to all the chimneys before the time expires!

Play here to support more games! https://play.idevgames.co.uk/game/60-second-santa-
